title: Duo partner for getting to silver
body: As the title says I am in need of a duo partner that could help me finish my 3 placement games and then play with me most days so I can get to silver. I will happily play most roles however I currently play a lot of jg and ad. Feel free to add me on (OCE) my name is WilliK

replies.body: Just finished my placement today... happy to duo, placed in bronze 2 atm, tank support main
